Package net_62v.external

package net_62v.external
  • Class
    Description
    IMundoProcessCallback
    Process callback interface, you can implement this interface for process lifecycle callback
    MetaActivityManager
    A class for components management, you can launch app by using this class.
    MetaApplicationInstaller
    A class for package management, you can clone a specific app by calling the MetaApplicationInstaller.cloneApp(String) method.
    You can install an app that not being installed on the host system by calling the MetaApplicationInstaller.installAppByPath(String) method.
    MetaCore
    Mundo core callback and process initializer
    MetaPackageManager
    A class for installed packages management.
    MetaStorageManager
    Mundo storage manager, you can use the storage related api by using this class.
